      16:35 Meydan Racecard on Friday 20 February 2026

      The 1M 209Y 16:35 BALANCHINE (Group 2) (Fillies and Mares) at Meydan will be run on Friday 20 February 2026. It is open to 4yo+ and has a prize fund of ..510,000. There are 7 runners.

      The market favourite for this race is DUBAI TREASURE (IRE), she is ridden by Oisin James Orr and trained by Saeed bin Suroor. Timeform's verdict for this race is BLUE NAZARE (IRE), she is ridden by William Buick and trained by Charlie Appleby.
